## Connections Module - English
connect-success = ✅ You are now connected to <b>{$chat}</b>. You can manage this group from my PM.
connect-usage = Usage: /connect <chat_id> or use /connect in a group directly.
connect-invalid-id = ❌ Invalid chat ID.
connect-no-admin = ❌ You need to be an admin in that group to connect.
disconnect-success = ✅ Disconnected from the group.
disconnect-not-connected = ❌ You are not connected to any group.
connection-status = 🔗 Currently connected to: <b>{$chat}</b> (<code>{$id}</code>)
connection-none = 🔗 You are not connected to any group. Use /connect <chat_id> or /connect in a group.
